Package: myman
Type: Package
Title: Draw from Sequence of 'My Man' Posts by Kevin Kruse
Version: 0.0.1.1
Date: 2026-07-21
Authors@R: person("Dirk", "Eddelbuettel", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "edd@debian.org",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6419-907X"))
Description: Starting on the afternoon of July 17, 2026, Kevin Kruse fired off an astonishing
 array of BlueSky replies to an initial post of his featuring a certain government figure:
 \url{https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:cnpe7qvcyjrhm6w7w7e4atur/post/3mqum4mxsuk2g}. All
 posts start with 'My man ...' and make for excellent input to a 'fortunes'-like package. So this
 small package obliges and offers a random draw each time its myman() function is called.
 The overall package structure follows package 'fortunes', and 'atrrr' was used to (bulk-)retrieve
 posts. Neither package is required to run this package to display random selections.
URL: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/myman, https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:cnpe7qvcyjrhm6w7w7e4atur/post/3mqum4mxsuk2g
BugReports: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/myman
